        <abstract> 
<p>Discussion of, and thanks for, CLB’s new work, <hi rend="italic">Races of the Old World</hi> [1863]. Special interest in p. 388 on colour and constitution; CD mentions questions sent previous year to surgeons serving in tropical countries regarding diseases and colour of hair and skin.</p> 
